I expected
a place where
they're serving

27:34.435 --> 27:36.524
grilled cheese
out of a little
window, you know.

27:36.524 --> 27:39.483
Yes, I suppose
they've fixed it up
over the years.

27:39.483 --> 27:41.572
But to us
it will
always be...

27:41.572 --> 27:43.270
The Shack.

27:43.270 --> 27:45.185
