29:08.485 --> 29:10.749
Is that all
you're gonna get?

29:10.749 --> 29:12.272
You're not
gonna get
a starter?

29:12.272 --> 29:14.100
Yeah, uh,
I'm just gonna

29:14.100 --> 29:15.405
stick with the middle
of the menu.

29:15.405 --> 29:17.190
All right,
suit yourself.

29:17.190 --> 29:18.626
Salvo, what are
you gonna get?

29:18.626 --> 29:20.846
Gloria, I think
I'm gonna have the...

29:20.846 --> 29:22.935
